<SYNC Start=544090><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=544597><P Class=KRCC>
당신이? 꽤 젊네
<SYNC Start=546958><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=547333><P Class=KRCC>
작년에 본청에 들어왔습니다
<SYNC Start=548625><P Class=KRCC>
