<SYNC Start=551015><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=551723><P Class=KRCC>
아까 교주님 말인데요<BR>어쩌실 생각이세요?
<SYNC Start=554813><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=554763><P Class=KRCC>
